{"tid":370763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遭Mel B狠批 Celine《全美一叮》眼濕濕 借女上位閪面","createTime":"2017-08-23T08:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T16:51:51.000Z","uid":48083,"like":82,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5694fb0f4ce4cdd057d02fe6962013dbf069a080","tid":370763,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T08:09:05.000Z","msg":"片： <a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20170823/542148\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20170823%2F542148&d=MZbb6wOW8NUOP6KiUv6%2B8BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=57ced64a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20170823%2F542148&h=c63c556a\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20170823/542148</a><br />\n<br />\n香港「小巨肺」譚芷昀（Celine Tam）由參與《全美一叮》開始一直深獲評判讚賞，不過Celine在半準決賽就被評判Mel B狠批她選錯曲，認為Celine未能唱出水準，超出她的能力範圍。<br />\n<br />\n人都對Celine的表現滿意，今次是Celine首次在比賽遇上劣評，搞到Celine不知如何反應，只能強顏歡笑，更一度眼濕濕，而譚順生在台下更是面色一沉。<br />\n<br />\nMel B的評言引來在場觀眾喝倒釆，不過其他評判未知是否心痛人仔細細的Celine唔開心，紛紛圍插Mel B，並為Celine護航，指她的聲音很好，又話她的天真可愛是其吸引之處，超模Heidi Klum更安慰話：「可以忘記她(Mel B)說的。」至於主腦Simon Cowell就話：「要記住佢只得9歲！你揀親嚟唱嘅都係金曲，尤其係下半部份控制得好，雖然你開頭有少少緊張。」"},{"pid":"22e7dd4db17fbf9ef2878f767e014365195a9c27","tid":370763,"uid":22422,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T08:14:04.000Z","msg":"呢個評判同沈智慧法官一樣<br />\n眼睛係雪亮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f330b47c694f0b1b8fb82f915a69e53c5ee2aa","tid":370763,"uid":34748,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T08:22:20.000Z","msg":"係唔係借個女上位嗰個？"},{"pid":"f624614cd4827f694ef5e2469475fdfbe3cf856c","tid":370763,"uid":22858,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T08:22:59.000Z","msg":"Mel B<img src=\"/ass